{"TopicId":212903,"ForumId":121,"TopicTitle":"Tiny Mouse Challenge-\u003EThe smallest Orbiter","CreatedByName":"The Dark Player","CreatedById":223678,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-26T03:08:08Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"The Dark Player","CreatedById":223678,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-26T03:08:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe challenge: In KSP or KSP2, make your smallest orbiter in terms of size or weight. Good Luck! (Mods are allowed but Kraken drives prohibited)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022;p\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/971609041_P.png\u0022 title=\u0022;p\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:valwink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/val_head_happywink.png\u0022 title=\u0022:valwink:\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:maneuver:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/Maneuver20px.png\u0022 title=\u0022:maneuver:\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://pickerwheel.com/pw?id=cg28U\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EThe picker wheel to see which category you are\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Klapaucius","CreatedById":181256,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-26T03:50:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224243222\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022212903\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221677380888\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022223678\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The Dark Player\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n41 minutes ago, The Dark Player said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe challenge: In KSP or KSP2, make your smallest orbiter in terms of size or weight. Good Luck! (Mods are allowed but Kraken drives prohibited)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022;p\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/971609041_P.png\u0022 title=\u0022;p\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:valwink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/val_head_happywink.png\u0022 title=\u0022:valwink:\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:maneuver:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/Maneuver20px.png\u0022 title=\u0022:maneuver:\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://pickerwheel.com/pw?id=cg28U\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EThe picker wheel to see which category you are\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI assume you mean size and weight including the launch vehicle?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Klapaucius","CreatedById":181256,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-26T05:17:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m not the best rocket builder, so this was a very good challenge for me. I\u0027m sure others can do much better.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTotal starting mass is 2.41 tonnes.\u00A0 It is 4.9 meters high.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00224E17Vec.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.63\u0022 height=\u0022641\u0022 width=\u00221132\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/4E17Vec.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022zRFMjrW.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002255.58\u0022 height=\u0022633\u0022 width=\u00221139\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/zRFMjrW.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Dark Player","CreatedById":223678,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-27T12:24:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGood!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"septemberWaves","CreatedById":160814,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-06T20:22:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224243222\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022212903\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221677380888\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022223678\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The Dark Player\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 2/26/2023 at 3:08 AM, The Dark Player said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe challenge: In KSP or KSP2, make your smallest orbiter in terms of size or weight. Good Luck! (Mods are allowed but Kraken drives prohibited)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022;p\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/971609041_P.png\u0022 title=\u0022;p\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:valwink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/val_head_happywink.png\u0022 title=\u0022:valwink:\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:maneuver:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/Maneuver20px.png\u0022 title=\u0022:maneuver:\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://pickerwheel.com/pw?id=cg28U\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EThe picker wheel to see which category you are\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have a couple of suggestions to make this challenge more interesting and appeal to more people:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nWhile the picker wheel is certainly novel, it disincentivises people from just choosing to optimize for whichever category they prefer (or from both categories), thus disincentivizing some people from trying the challenge altogether.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nThe \u0022minimum size\u0022 category needs to be more clearly defined. Do you just care about height, or diameter, or do you care about all dimensions? I assume the latter, but it\u0027s not clear at all.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nThe \u0022minimum size\u0022 category should have \u003Cem\u003Estrict\u003C/em\u003E restrictions on part clipping. Without such limitations, the challenge is reduced to an exercise in clipping as much as possible into the volume of the smallest fuel tank and sticking a command seat in there too.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nBecause this challenge is all about optimization of a craft, I recommend separating stock and modded leaderboards - specifically, craft with any modded parts (not that any exist now, but they certainly will in future) or any mods which change the game\u0027s behaviour (in particular, its physics) \u003Cem\u003Emust\u003C/em\u003E be judged separately, because otherwise the challenge is not fair. It also may be wise to pre-emptively ban any mods that adjust physics or add parts altogether, or (if you really want to allow part mods) limit any part mods to ones which are \u003Cem\u003Ebalanced like stock parts\u003C/em\u003E.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Dark Player","CreatedById":223678,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-07T12:21:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOkay, but this challenge is stock\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:cry:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/cry.png\u0022 title=\u0022:cry:\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"septemberWaves","CreatedById":160814,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-07T14:59:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224253888\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022212903\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221678191717\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022223678\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The Dark Player\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, The Dark Player said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOkay, but this challenge is stock\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:cry:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/cry.png\u0022 title=\u0022:cry:\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot according to the challenge:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224243222\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022212903\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221677380888\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022223678\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The Dark Player\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 2/26/2023 at 3:08 AM, The Dark Player said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMods are allowed\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you want the challenge to be stock-only, you may want to rewrite it to say so.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-03-07T15:00:14Z\u0022 title=\u002203/07/2023 03:00  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 7, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by septemberWaves\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Periple","CreatedById":225622,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-07T19:57:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI got 8 parts, 0.50 tons, 2.29 m x 0.63 m x 0.63 m. I don\u0027t think I can do much better than that.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022?imw=1024\u0026amp;imh=576\u0026amp;ima=fit\u0026amp;impolicy=Lette\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.25\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022 src=\u0022https://steamuserimages-a.akamaihd.net/ugc/2013709931137195422/9C617CE7CEB0C5EFE424F788D34CCF7D60AF824F/?imw=1024\u0026amp;imh=576\u0026amp;ima=fit\u0026amp;impolicy=Letterbox\u0026amp;imcolor=%23000000\u0026amp;letterbox=true\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022?imw=5000\u0026amp;imh=5000\u0026amp;ima=fit\u0026amp;impolicy=Lett\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022166.67\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://steamuserimages-a.akamaihd.net/ugc/2013709931137196841/7741937035386C2AF0F918CEAA5886E2198F4D33/?imw=5000\u0026amp;imh=5000\u0026amp;ima=fit\u0026amp;impolicy=Letterbox\u0026amp;imcolor=%23000000\u0026amp;letterbox=false\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Dark Player","CreatedById":223678,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-10T10:18:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPeriple is currently 1st\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ctable border=\u00221\u0022 cellpadding=\u00221\u0022 cellspacing=\u00221\u0022 style=\u0022width:500px;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ctbody\u003E\n\u003Ctr\u003E\n\u003Ctd\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/td\u003E\n\u003Ctd\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/td\u003E\n\u003C/tr\u003E\n\u003Ctr\u003E\n\u003Ctd\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/td\u003E\n\u003Ctd\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/td\u003E\n\u003C/tr\u003E\n\u003C/tbody\u003E\n\u003C/table\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AdamKSP","CreatedById":228142,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-22T18:23:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHey everyone...new here.\u00A0 Figured I\u0027d toss my hat into the ring on this one...was tough, but got it smaller...\u003Cimg alt=\u0022?imw=5000\u0026amp;imh=5000\u0026amp;ima=fit\u0026amp;impolicy=Lett\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://steamuserimages-a.akamaihd.net/ugc/2046362392235208024/3595174ED1AB5783B8D216D405AD908B309604D0/?imw=5000\u0026amp;imh=5000\u0026amp;ima=fit\u0026amp;impolicy=Letterbox\u0026amp;imcolor=%23000000\u0026amp;letterbox=false\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022?imw=5000\u0026amp;imh=5000\u0026amp;ima=fit\u0026amp;impolicy=Lett\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://steamuserimages-a.akamaihd.net/ugc/2046362392235207904/4BFBD370E7A95A80FC9755CDEF698740321CCE17/?imw=5000\u0026amp;imh=5000\u0026amp;ima=fit\u0026amp;impolicy=Letterbox\u0026amp;imcolor=%23000000\u0026amp;letterbox=false\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dunas Only Moon","CreatedById":224915,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-13T16:47:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/228142-adamksp/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 da